quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  76,6,"This will be a gushing spring wherefrom Allah's servants shall drink wine, a spring from which they will take out channels wherever they wish.",footnotes:182466:1,footnotes:182467:2,footnotes:182468:3
  76,7,"These will be the ones who fulfil their vows and dread the Day whose woe shall be spread far and wide;",footnotes:182469:1
  76,8,"those who, for the love of Him, feed the needy, and the orphan, and the captive,",footnotes:182470:1,footnotes:182471:2
  76,9,"(saying): “We feed you only for Allah's sake; we do not seek of you any recompense or thanks,",footnotes:182472:1,footnotes:182473:2
  76,10,"we fear from our Lord a Day that shall be long and distressful.”"